title: Project2612 Genesis VGM Music Archive
description:
Project2612 Genesis VGM Music Archive

This set of files includes an archive of Project2612 VGM Genesis and Mega Drive music files, another file with updates and additions since it&#039;s creation, a winamp plugin that can play these files, and a version of winamp that&#039;s compatible with the plugin.

VGM is a logged music format that allows songs to be looped the way they are in the game, and it&#039;s also much smaller than an encoded recording of the same music in most cases.

project2612.org is where you can find the original files at, as well as related information. It&#039;s a hassle to try to download every individual game, and their tracker isn&#039;t working yet.
